This folder included: 

(1) The results with the best architectures for four data (*_FINAL.xls);

(2) MAF files for four data that calculated with the standard way;

(3) The statistical significance test results for non-regularized and regularized ResNets on different data (S5-S8); '

(4) Ablation study and informativenness analysis for the models with dual-factors (S5). The method, results and the analysis/findings have been included as well. Because of the limitation of word, it was not included in the main manuscript. 
